/**
 * Asynchronous, global, and persistent key-value storage. Storage limit is 10 MB per domain, which may be shared by multiple add-ins.
 *
 * @remarks
 *
 * Will be deprecated in the future, please use Office.Storage instead.
 */
members.name: AsyncStorage

members.docComment:
/**
 * Retrieves all keys and invokes a callback when finished. Returns a Promise.
 *
 * @param  - callback
 */
members.name: getAllKeys

members.docComment:
/**
 * Retrieves an item by key, then issues a callback. Returns a Promise.
 *
 * @param key - The name of the key to retrieve. Must be a string.
 *
 * @param callback - Returned result is a string.
 */
members.name: getItem

members.docComment:
/**
 * Retrieves multiple items from storage and invokes a callback when finished. Returns a Promise.
 *
 * @param keys - Keys of the items to be retrieved. Must be an array of strings.
 *
 * @param  - callback
 */
members.name: multiGet

members.docComment:
/**
 * Removes multiple items from storage and invokes a callback when finished. Returns a Promise.
 *
 * @param keys - Keys of the items to be removed. Must be an array of strings.
 *
 * @param  - callback
 */
members.name: multiRemove

members.docComment:
/**
 * Sets multiple key-value pairs and invokes a callback when finished. Returns a Promise.
 *
 * @param keyValuePairs - Must be arrays of strings.
 *
 * @param  - callback
 */
members.name: multiSet

members.docComment:
/**
 * Removes items by key and invokes a callback when finished. It returns a Promise that resolves to an object containing the keys and values requested.
 *
 * @param key - The key of the item to be removed. Must be a string.
 *
 * @param  - callback
 */
members.name: removeItem

members.docComment:
/**
 * Creates a new key-value pair in storage or updates an existing key with a new value. Returns a Promise.
 *
 * @param key - The name of the key for the key-value pair. Must be a string.
 *
 * @param value - The name of the value. Must be a string.
 *
 * @param  - callback
 */
members.name: setItem

members.docComment:
/**
 * Asynchronous, global, and persistent key-value storage.
 *
 * @remarks
 *
 * Storage limit is 10 MB per domain, which may be shared by multiple add-ins.
 */
members.name: Storage

members.docComment:
/**
 * Retrieves an item from storage based on its key. Returns a Promise. In the event the Promise does not resolve, returns null.
 *
 * @param key - Key of item to be retrieved. Must be a string.
 */
members.name: getItem

members.docComment:
/**
 * Retrieves multiple items from storage based on their key. Returns a Promise. In the event the Promise does not resolve, returns null.
 *
 * @param keys - Keys of items to be removed. Must be an array of strings.
 */
members.name: getItems
getKeys

members.docComment:
/**
 * Removes an item from storage based on its key. Returns a Promise.
 *
 * @param key - Key of item to be removed. Must be a string.
 */
members.name: removeItem

members.docComment:
/**
 * Removes multiple items from storage. Returns a Promise.
 *
 * @param keys - Keys of items to be removed. Must be an array of strings.
 */
members.name: removeItems

members.docComment:
/**
 * Sets a key-value pair into storage or updates an existing key-value pair. Returns a Promise.
 *
 * @param key - Key of item to be set. Must be a string.
 *
 * @param value - Must be a string.
 */
members.name: setItem

members.docComment:
/**
 * Sets multiple items into storage or updates multiple items within storage. Returns a Promise.
 *
 * @param keyValues - Key-value pairs to be set. Must be strings.
 */
members.name: setItems
AsyncStorage
